ews/music/glastonbury-2024-rumours-spread-of-secret-coldplay-show-at-local-venue-3769280">有人猜测酷玩乐队将在格拉斯顿伯里当地的一个场地举行秘密表演</a>。乐队即将在“值得农场”(Worthy Farm) 上亮相，歌迷们认为，在大型舞台卡车和乐队的装备出现在场馆后，他们可能会在弗罗姆的 Cheese &amp; Grain 进行一场热身表演。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.somersetlive.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife/coldplay-glastonbury-venue-rehearsal-music-9371951" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SomersetLive</em></a>报道称乐队只是在那里排练。该场地还发表了一份声明，揭示了：“我们正在收到大量查询在会场上秘密格拉斯顿伯里节目的潜力的询问。我们可以明确地指出，直到周日在欧洲橄榄油2024年欧洲欧洲像欧洲欧洲银行（UEFA EURO）进行16轮比赛之前，奶酪和谷物中根本不会发生任何活动。 </p><figure id="attachment_3518257" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3518257" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3518257" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518257" class="wp-caption-text">汤姆·奥克斯利（Tom Oxley）拍摄的孟买自行车俱乐部</figcaption></figure><p>“对于那些有幸在周末前往格拉斯顿伯里节日的人来说，我们希望您度过了不可思议的时间，喝了很多水！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bookies-odds-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-kasabian-kings-of-leon-pulp-3762814">整个周末，格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）现场还有许多其他秘密套装</a>，卡萨比亚（Kasabian）在周六填补了TBA插槽的最爱。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-gates-to-glastonbury-2024-have-just-opened-3768713">Glastonbury 2024年的大门昨天（6月26日，星期三）开放</a>，在来自Headliners <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">Sza</a>之类的音乐周末之前，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-talks-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-honour-of-my-life-3600979">Shania Twain的传奇插槽</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a>的表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna</a> ，Burna，Burna，Burna，Burna，Burna <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-marie">Anne-Marie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">Camila Cabello</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/masego">Masego</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>等等。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">在这里查看完整的阵容。</a></p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-2024-set-clash-guide-3766391">以下是今年预计最严重的冲突</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-weather-forecast-3763664">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新天气预报</a>。</p><p> <em><a